## Work-Precision Diagrams

### High Tolerances

Final-value error at the end of the integration interval.

```julia
abstols = 1.0 ./ 10.0 .^ (5:8)
reltols = 1.0 ./ 10.0 .^ (1:4)

setups = [
    Dict(:prob_choice => 1, :alg => Rosenbrock23()),
    Dict(:prob_choice => 1, :alg => Rodas4()),
    Dict(:prob_choice => 1, :alg => FBDF()),
    Dict(:prob_choice => 1, :alg => QNDF()),
]

wp = WorkPrecisionSet(probs, abstols, reltols, setups;
    save_everystep = false, appxsol = refs, maxiters = Int(2e4), numruns = 1)
plot(wp)
```

```julia
abstols = 1.0 ./ 10.0 .^ (6:8)
reltols = 1.0 ./ 10.0 .^ (2:4)

setups = [
    Dict(:prob_choice => 1, :alg => Rosenbrock23()),
    Dict(:prob_choice => 1, :alg => Rodas4()),
]

wp = WorkPrecisionSet(probs, abstols, reltols, setups;
    save_everystep = false, appxsol = refs, maxiters = Int(2e4), numruns = 1)
plot(wp)
```

